  "title": "Administrative Assistant",
  "description": "<p>Requirement: :      </p><p>1. Office Hour - 8:30am to 5:30pm      </p><p>2. Proficient in Microsoft Software Applications      </p><p>3. At least 4 Years of working experience and have experience in the related field is required for this position.      </p><p>4. Candidate must possess at least Secondary in any field.      </p><p>5. Able to communicate in written and verbal for English and Chinese         </p><p><br /></p><p>Job Description :      </p><p>1. Prepare invoice for private job claim.      </p><p>2. Process photo management of work, private drawing and calculation of drawing work done.      </p><p>3. Tabulate and email documents as required by customer for claiming.      </p><p>4. Carrying out administrative tasks such as date entries to excel summary.      </p><p>5. Issue quotation as required.      </p><p>6. Process billing and purchases related to Premix, Millwaste.      </p><p>7. Maintain an effective filling system for ease of retrieval and keeping of information.      </p><p>8. Perform any others tasks that may be assigned to you from time to time by the Company.</p>",
